<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Success</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #28a745;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for your payment of Rs. 20000, <strong><%= username %></strong>.</p>
        <p>Your payment ID is <strong><%= payment_id %></strong>.</p>
        <p>You can now <a href="/auth/login">login</a> to your account.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
